命令1：
drop database <数据库名>;
例子：
mysql> DROP DATABASE database_2
    -> ;
Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.05 sec)
命令2： mysqladmin -u root -p drop <数据库名>
例子：
C:\WINDOWS\system32>mysqladmin -u root -p DROP database_1
Enter password: ************
Dropping the database is potentially a very bad thing to do.
Any data stored in the database will be destroyed.

Do you really want to drop the 'database_1' database [y/N] y
Database "database_1" dropped
//注意：被删除的数据库中的数据将永久消失。
